      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spread <strong>half</strong> the<strong> tomato sauce</strong> over the <strong>chicken</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>grated cheese</strong> and <strong>torn mozzarella</strong></p><p>Dollop the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>tomato sauce</strong> over the top</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and all of the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>chicken parmigiana</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
