      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, tear your<strong> basil</strong> into a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong> (save a little for garnish) and grind to a paste</p><p>Tip: Don't have a pestle & mortar? Pulse in a food processor instead!</p><p>Stir your <strong>mayo</strong> through the <strong>basil</strong> <strong>paste </strong>– this is your <strong>basil mayo</strong></p>",
