    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>ciabatta halves</strong> to a <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once toasted, spread the <strong>ciabatta</strong> with the <strong>basil mayo</strong> and top with the <strong>chicken parmigiana</strong> and <strong>remaining torn basil</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>open chicken parmigiana sarnie</strong> with the <strong>fries</strong> and <strong>baby leaf salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a crack of <strong>black pepper</strong> to the salad</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
